703130f-c.text:
(1) Bay 20th Street, at the S.W. corner of Benson Ave. A view of the St. Dunbar [sic; Finbar?] R.C. Church. Benson Ave., is at right foreground.
January 11, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.

(2) The same, from another angle,
January 11, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.

(3) The same, showing also a frame house at No. 133 Bay 20th Street.
anuary 11, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
